  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Heavy rain today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Meteorological Department has announced that heavy rainfall of more than 150 mm is expected in many parts of the country today.",
        "There is a possibility of developing a low atmospheric fog in the areas surrounding Sri Lanka.",
        "Occasional rain or thundershowers are likely in most parts of the country.",
        "Heavy rainfall of more than 150 mm is expected at some places in the Upper, Southern, Sabaragamuwa, Central and Uva provinces.",
        "Heavy rainfall of over 100 mm is expected at some places in other parts of the country. (a)"
      ],
